{
  "subject": "Proposal for Mobile App Prototype – Alex Doe",
  "body": "<p>Dear Sarah Johnson,</p><p>I’m excited to submit my proposal for your <strong>Mobile App Prototype for Fitness Tracker</strong> project. With 4+ years of experience building cross‑platform mobile applications using React Native—and a recent project (HealthSync App) that integrated Google Fit—I’m confident I can deliver a high‑quality prototype that meets your timeline and functional requirements.</p><p><strong>Proposed Scope &amp; Deliverables</strong><br>- Onboarding screen with brand‑consistent UI<br>- Secure login/authentication (email &amp; social options)<br>- Dashboard displaying real‑time activity metrics<br>- Activity summary screen with Google Fit data integration<br>- Full source code and documentation</p><p><strong>Timeline</strong>: 3 weeks (starting upon project kickoff)<br><strong>Fixed Price</strong>: <strong>$1,400</strong><br>This quote reflects a competitive rate (≈ $18.75/hr) based on the current US market average of $71.5/hr for React Native work, while ensuring high quality and rapid delivery.</p><p>I look forward to discussing any specifics you’d adjust. Thank you for considering my proposal.</p><p>Best regards,<br>Alex Doe<br>React Native Developer<br>Phone: (555) 123‑4567<br><a href=\"https://portfolio.example.com/alexdoe\">Portfolio</a></p>"
}
